name: Eerie Compression
summary: Your limbs and even your torso can collapse in on themselves, allowing you to fit through tight spaces as though you were a Small creature.
description:
Your limbs and even your torso can collapse in on themselves, allowing you to fit through tight spaces as though you were a Small creature. You can move at full Speed while Squeezing.Traits

Fleshwarp: A humanoid transformed so completely by outside forces that they are now a unique ancestry
